### REST Client requests for Proaktiv Dokument Hub
### Secrets are loaded from .vscode/settings.json (gitignored)
### See: https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=humao.rest-client

@hubBaseUrl = https://proatest.qa.vitecnext.no
@installationId = MSPROATEST
@backendUrl = http://localhost:8000

# For secrets, add to .vscode/settings.json (create if missing):
# {
#   "rest-client.environmentVariables": {
#     "$shared": {},
#     "qa": {
#       "hubProductLogin": "YOUR_PRODUCT_LOGIN",
#       "hubAccessKey": "YOUR_ACCESS_KEY"
#     }
#   }
# }

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────
### VITEC HUB API
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Verify Product Access
# @name accountMethods
GET {{hubBaseUrl}}/Account/Methods
Authorization: Basic {{hubProductLogin}}:{{hubAccessKey}}

###

### Get Departments (Offices)
# @name departments
GET {{hubBaseUrl}}/{{installationId}}/Departments
Authorization: Basic {{hubProductLogin}}:{{hubAccessKey}}

###

### Get Employees
# @name employees
GET {{hubBaseUrl}}/{{installationId}}/Employees
Authorization: Basic {{hubProductLogin}}:{{hubAccessKey}}

###

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────
### BACKEND API (Local)
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Sync Offices from Vitec Hub
POST {{backendUrl}}/api/offices/sync

###

### Sync Employees from Vitec Hub
POST {{backendUrl}}/api/employees/sync

###

### List all Offices
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/offices

###

### List all Employees
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/employees

###

### Health Check
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/health
